    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gather Chakra into your weapon, refining it into a spiritual edge that you swing down, creating a shimmering, golden ray. If it hits an animal, elemental, humanoid, magical beast, monstrous humanoid or outsider, it deals 2d6 force damage. You may use this technique as a full-round action instead. If you do, instead of firing a ray, you swing your sword and make a melee attack that will deal 2d6 additional force damage if it hits a creature of the appropriate creature type.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 10d6 damage total.</p>\n\n",
